1) Fairview Heights & Monroe Avenue Elementary Schools and
Richmond Community College are located less than 1 mile
from the studied intersection and were in session on the date
of the count, as were all Richmond County Schools.
2) Pedestrians were observed and counted – none were
4) Area lighting was present at the count location.
5) No highway construction was observed that impacted normal traffic patterns.
6) Data collection equipment was operating correctly at time of count.
7) Counter took breaks from 9:00 – 9:15 AM and 1:30 – 2:00 PM. Data for these periods was interpolated.
8) The counter did not have any additional notes.
